casebody.data:
IN RE ADOPTION OF N.J.A.C. 17:1-6.4, 17:1-7.5 and 17:1-7.10. (New Jersey Education Association - Petitioner) C-291 September Term 2018
081374 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 16, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002171-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
